            "nodes": [
                {
                    "id": "h_intro_narration",
                    "speaker": "narrator",
                    "text": "First day of the new semester. The hallway feels a little louder, a little brighter... and full of posters you never noticed before."
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_noticeboard",
                    "speaker": "narrator",
                    "text": "SUSTAINABILITY WEEK – Talks, clean-up events, food bank volunteering. Sign up at the cafeteria."
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_friends_start",
                    "speaker": "friendA",
                    "text": "Oi, over here! You saw all the new posters around campus?",
                    "choices": [
                        {
                            "id": "h_choice_seen_posters",
                            "text": "Yeah, something about SDGs, right?",
                            "sdgDelta": 5,
                            "setFlags": [
                                "interest_sdg_positive"
                            ],
                            "nextNodeId": "h_explain_positive"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "h_choice_not_sure",
                            "text": "Not really… what’s SDG?",
                            "sdgDelta": 3,
                            "setFlags": [
                                "interest_sdg_neutral"
                            ],
                            "nextNodeId": "h_explain_neutral"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "h_choice_extra_work",
                            "text": "Looks like extra work to me.",
                            "sdgDelta": 0,
                            "setFlags": [
                                "interest_sdg_indifferent"
                            ],
                            "nextNodeId": "h_explain_pushback"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_explain_positive",
                    "speaker": "friendA",
                    "text": "Yeah! Sustainable Development Goals. The uni is doing a whole week about it.",
                    "autoNext": "h_explain_positive_b"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_explain_positive_b",
                    "speaker": "friendB",
                    "text": "They’re doing talks, clean-ups, even something with the campus food bank.",
                    "autoNext": "h_friends_wrapup"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_explain_neutral",
                    "speaker": "friendB",
                    "text": "SDG stands for Sustainable Development Goals. Stuff like education, equality, climate…",
                    "autoNext": "h_explain_neutral_b"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_explain_neutral_b",
                    "speaker": "friendA",
                    "text": "You might not know yet, but even small actions matter here on campus.",
                    "autoNext": "h_friends_wrapup"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_explain_pushback",
                    "speaker": "friendA",
                    "text": "Maybe. But if we’re already stuck here studying, might as well make it mean something.",
                    "autoNext": "h_explain_pushback_b"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_explain_pushback_b",
                    "speaker": "friendB",
                    "text": "You don’t have to save the whole world lah, just do something small.",
                    "autoNext": "h_friends_wrapup"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_friends_wrapup",
                    "speaker": "friendA",
                    "text": "Anyway, the lecturer said today’s class is about it. If we’re late, that one is on you.",
                    "autoNext": "h_objective_update"
                },
                {
                    "id": "h_objective_update",
                    "speaker": "system",
                    "text": "New objective: Go to class to learn how SDGs relate to your campus life.",
                    "onComplete": {
                        "setFlags": [
                            "chapter1_scene1_dialogue_done",
                            "{major_choice_flag}"
                        ],
                        "unlockExit": true,
                        "points": 2
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "classroom",
            "backgroundKey": "bgClassroom",
            "startNodeId": "c_intro_prof",
            "exitUnlockedFlag": "chapter1_scene2_exit_unlocked",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "id": "c_intro_prof",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "Good morning, everyone. Today we’re going to talk about something bigger than grades: the Sustainable Development Goals.",
                    "autoNext": "c_prof_explain"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_prof_explain",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "There are 17 SDGs. They cover poverty, education, climate, equality… and we’ll connect them to your lives here on campus.",
                    "autoNext": "c_prof_question"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_prof_question",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "Be honest. How many of you think students like you can make a difference?",
                    "choices": [
                        {
                            "id": "c_choice_confident",
                            "text": "If we work together, yeah.",
                            "sdgDelta": 5,
                            "setFlags": [
                                "confidence_positive"
                            ],
                            "nextNodeId": "c_prof_answer_confident"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "c_choice_unsure",
                            "text": "Maybe? But it feels far from us.",
                            "sdgDelta": 3,
                            "setFlags": [
                                "confidence_neutral"
                            ],
                            "nextNodeId": "c_prof_answer_unsure"
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "c_choice_dismissive",
                            "text": "I don’t think we can do much.",
                            "sdgDelta": -1,
                            "setFlags": [
                                "confidence_negative"
                            ],
                            "nextNodeId": "c_prof_answer_dismissive"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_prof_answer_confident",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "Exactly. Change starts with small groups taking things seriously. Campus is perfect for experimenting.",
                    "autoNext": "c_prof_foodbank"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_prof_answer_unsure",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "It can feel distant. That’s why your projects this semester focus on real issues around you.",
                    "autoNext": "c_prof_foodbank"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_prof_answer_dismissive",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "I get that reaction a lot. By the end of the semester, I hope you’ll prove yourself wrong.",
                    "autoNext": "c_prof_foodbank"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_prof_foodbank",
                    "speaker": "professor",
                    "text": "Some seniors worked with the campus food bank last year, helping redistribute surplus food to students who needed it.",
                    "autoNext": "c_friend_whisper"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_friend_whisper",
                    "speaker": "friend",
                    "text": "(whispers) Food bank actually sounds kind of interesting, doesn’t it?",
                    "autoNext": "c_system_idea"
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_system_idea",
                    "speaker": "system",
                    "text": "New idea unlocked: Campus Food Bank.",
                    "onComplete": {
                        "setFlags": [
                            "chapter1_scene2_dialogue_done",
                            "{major_choice_flag}"
                        ],
                        "unlockExit": true,
                        "points": 3
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_bench_1",
                    "inspectDialogueId": "inspect_c_bench_1",
                    "speaker": "student",
                    "text": "Honestly… I thought SDGs were just another poster thing. But the food bank example is real.",
                    "sdgDelta": 1
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_poster_sdg4",
                    "inspectDialogueId": "inspect_c_poster_sdg4",
                    "speaker": "system",
                    "text": "Poster: SDG 4 — Quality Education. Education isn't just exams; it’s access, support, and equal opportunity.",
                    "sdgDelta": 2
                },
                {
                    "id": "c_poster_sdg13",
                    "inspectDialogueId": "inspect_c_poster_sdg13",
                    "speaker": "system",
                    "text": "Poster: SDG 13 — Climate Action. Small campus habits add up: energy use, waste, transport choices.",
                    "sdgDelta": 2
                }
            ]
